  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "西蒙诺夫 SKS 7.62x39 卡宾枪",
      "en": "TOZ Simonov SKS 7.62x39 carbine"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "SKS",
      "en": "SKS"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 47,734₽ | 物品价值: 19,331 | Mechanic报价: 10,825₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 34,305₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级3 < GP x23 | Σ ≈ 172,500₽\n购买渠道 @ Prapor 等级1 < 29,914₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > A Friend From the East @ 莲花\n\n配方需要 x1 > 武器零件 x1 @ 工作台 等级1 < … | Δ ≈ -25,198₽\n\n由谢尔盖·西蒙诺夫为7.62x39弹设计的苏联半自动卡宾枪，在国外被称为SKS-45，它在独联体和西方国家里都非常流行。目前一些国家仍在通过仿造和改造的方式，使该型武器继续服役。这把特殊的枪来自图拉兵工厂的扩展仓库，并且从未经受民用武器标准化程序处理。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 47,734₽ | 物品价值: 19,331 | Mechanic报价: 10,825₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 34,305₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级3 < GP x23 | Σ ≈ 172,500₽\n购买渠道 @ Prapor 等级1 < 29,914₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > A Friend From the East @ 莲花\n\n配方需要 x1 > 武器零件 x1 @ 工作台 等级1 < … | Δ ≈ -25,198₽\n\nA Soviet semi-automatic carbine designed by Sergei Simonov for 7.62x39 cartridges and known abroad as SKS-45. Immensely popular both in CIS countries and in the West, this weapon is still in active service in some countries in form of various copies and modifications. This particular model comes from extended storage warehouses of Tula Arms Plant and haven't yet undergone the civilian weapon normalization procedure."
    },
